inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-aws-profile-role-nodeLaunchConfiguration-06391b1
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-04a70ff88ae18170d","subnet-0275a69685c142c08","subnet-0c2470e65898ba412"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-9296f04-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-9296f04
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
